data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this GORGEOUS 3-level townhome in Lorton!  Freshly painted.  New  LVT flooring in main floor.  New stainless-steel refrigerator, range and microwave.  Lovely, covered front porch.  The first level offers an open floor plan with two-sided gas fireplace, kitchen, living room and powder room.   Two spacious bedrooms and a full bath await you in the second floor.  Primary suite in the top floor for ultimate privacy.  Primary bedroom with coffered ceiling, ceiling fan, walk-in closet and private bathroom. Two assigned parking spaces (#71), and 2 visitor passes.  Condo fee includes water, amenities include outdoor-pool, fitness center, club house and much more!! Great location! Don't miss out!!  Close to shopping centers, an array of dining options, and major transportation routes, I95, Fairfax County Parkway.
